                        <note rend="inline" type="source">893.512/639: Telegram</note>
                        <head><hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to
                                the Chargé in China</hi> (<persName type="to"><hi rend="italic">Mayer</hi></persName>)</head>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1927-08-19T16:00:00-04:00"><hi rend="italic">August 19,
                                        1927—4 p.m.</hi></date></dateline></opener>
                        <p>320. Your 819, August 19, 1 p.m. Department approves your reply to
                            Shanghai as set forth in paragraph 2.</p>
                        <closer><signed><hi rend="smallcaps">Kellogg</hi></signed></closer>
